'''Yarkora''' was the native language of the [[Yarkora/Legends|Yarkora]] [[Species/Legends|species]]. It was never spoken in the presence of non-Yarkora.

All Yarkora found on the [[The galaxy/Legends|galaxy]] were fluent in both Yarkora and [[Galactic Basic Standard/Legends|Basic]], although they were only literate in their own language.

